<br>
/applaud witherweaver<br>
<br>
So a level 65 person with 40aa's transfers over here, and applies to and is accepted to F&amp;F.  How will he effect you?  He likely won't.  You will likely never see him, becasue he's having fun in the Elemental planes/plane of time while you're RPing with your guild in Nektulos/lake rathe.  So he adds two more items to the bazaar at lower prices.  That's two more items *you* can now buy with your hard earned plat, without having to visit the upper planes yourself.  He wins, you win.<br>
<br>
Until a pure RP guild is in position to contest against F&amp;F or their ilk, saying that they are infringing on our rights as roleplayers is BS.  They are essentially using a part of the game we roleplayers can not normally utilize.  I have yet to have a person harass me for roleplaying, and I do so openly, by the banks in PoK.  So, perhaps I'm just young and naive, or perhaps I'm just not old and jaded.<br>
<br>
What if F&amp;F wasn't here?  Then the PoT and elemental planes would likely be empty, and many items which we buy in the bazaar would not be there.  Many staples to our economy as it is now would vanish, and Sony would have even less reason to listen to any of us at all. <br>
<br>
Well met, F&amp;F.  Enjoy your planes as I enjoy my stories. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=689507"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/b_angel517/images/sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
