You my friend can whine bitch rant and rave all you want and you know what it doesnt mean anything in the long run, becasue in  the end you are just a bunch of spoiled little kids in mentality if not nessecarrily in age who expect to get far more than they deserve. You are owed nothing more or less than anyone else who pays the monthly fee is to play on this game despite whatever little misconception you may have concoted in your tiny little head.<br>
