and to be honest I read the soapbox almost daily and the good majority of grieving drama and otehr bullshit comes from peopel I would consider a part of teh roleplay community, so maybe it is time for a collective reevaluation of the word d00d, does it just mean someone that talks in l33t, or is it an overbearing rude asshole who trains his guards on you for &quot;role-playing his character&quot; personally I dont care for either  but both are on this server and both will continue to come irregardless of whatever little temper tantrum you throw <br>
