<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;... for death awaits you all with nasty, big, pointy teeth. - Tim the Enchanter</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elsbetsquishytoes>elsbet squishytoes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Grey</span><br>  Posts: 911<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/19/03 5:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3496.topic&index=137>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: sooooooo</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I of course would appreciate some well thought out responses, but hell it's the soapbox.. flame away! <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
