<br>
Alright.  Seriously, people do make this the RP server.  Unfortunately we have less and less of them as time goes by.  I am not beating the drum of Dead Roleplay here, though, because I still have fun, and new blood wanders in to the roleplaying guilds often enough to keep me happy.  Ubers will always do their thing, but they still have enough folks like Rhatha, Jebbar, Dalion, and Ayrielle to keep up the nature of our server.<br>
<br>
Nuts like me can come here, screw around, and do pretty well for themselves without being hollered at.  Roleplayers can find a home here.  Numnut d00dz can come here, too, and do their thing, which totally sucks, go the hell away, you have 40 some other servers to fart around on.  But stick around.  Norrather's Call needs members, I guess. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
We really do have the best group of folks that any collection of random EQ players could hope for, though, so this is where I will play until I get bored of the game, which seems a long way off.  There is, in general, a quality to our players that I certainly never saw on Veeshan, and thanks to most of you that play here.  Well done. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
